schools.name: John E. Flynn A Marzano Academy

data.description:
Welcome to your own personal haven in the heart of Westminster, Colorado! This captivating single-family home offers a blend of comfort, style, and untapped potential. With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1,416 square feet of living space, this residence is a hidden gem waiting to be discovered.

Step inside and be greeted by an inviting open floor plan that effortlessly combines functionality and warmth. The heart of the home is the stunning kitchen, where sleek granite countertops and gleaming stainless steel appliances take center stage. Whip up culinary masterpieces while entertaining friends and family, creating memories that will last a lifetime.

Indulge in the luxury of a private master suite, tucked away upstairs for ultimate tranquility. The en-suite bathroom provides a sanctuary for relaxation, allowing you to unwind after a long day. Downstairs, two additional bedrooms offer versatility and comfort, accommodating loved ones or creating space for a home office or hobby room.

Imagine waking up each day to the possibilities offered by a home that underwent a transformative remodel just two years ago. The updated flooring adds a touch of elegance, while the granite countertops and stainless steel appliances enhance the overall aesthetic. Embrace the opportunity to make this home uniquely yours with your personal touches and creative vision.

Spanning an impressive 1/4 acre lot, this property boasts endless potential for outdoor living. Whether you dream of cultivating a lush garden oasis, creating a play area for little ones, or envision a future garage to house your prized vehicles, the expansive space allows for all your aspirations to become a reality.

While this home requires some TLC and maintenance to restore it to its full glory, the possibilities are boundless. Unleash your imagination and transform this diamond in the rough into a true masterpiece that reflects your unique style and preferences.
